		<title>Ethereum Virtual Machine Bytecode: The Language of Smart Contracts</title>
		<link>https://securenest.org/learn/ethereum-virtual-machine-bytecode</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jordan Adams]]></dc:creator>
